title: Andrew Sheets:  The Fed’s Great Expectations Quandary
description: On today's podcast, Markets met the Fed rate cut with a collective shrug. Could investor expectations make it harder for the Fed to succeed? Chief Cross-Asset Strategist Andrew Sheets provides analysis.
